Bellatrix

Bellatrix Exploration Ltd. is a growth oriented oil and gas company operating in Western Canada’s Sedimentary Basin. The Company focuses on operating with integrity and conducting operations in a safe and environmentally responsible manner while providing sustained shareholder growth in value. Our land base is focused in west central Alberta, Canada.    View more View more 






